{"ID":270344, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"344\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs343.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs345.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 344<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">time henceforth occupy your attention. The Scriptures inform us that &ldquo;This is life eternal that they\n  might know thee, the only true God, and Jesus Christ whom thou hast sent.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">If any man does not know God,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> and inquires what kind of a being he is,&mdash;if he will search\n  diligently his own heart<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span>&mdash;if the declaration of Jesus and the apostles be true, he will realize that he\n  has not eternal life;<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> for there can be eternal life on no other principle.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">My first object is to find out the character of the only wise and true God,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> and what kind of a\n  being he is; and if I am so fortunate as to be the man to comprehend God,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and explain or convey\n  the principles to your hearts, so that the Spirit seals<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> them upon you, then let every man and woman\n  henceforth sit in silence,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> put their hands on their mouths,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> and never lift their hands<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> or voices,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span>\n  or say anything against the man of God<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> or the servants of God<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> again. But if I fail to do it, it\n  becomes my duty to renounce all further pretensions to revelations and inspirations, or to be a\n  prophet; and I should be like the rest of the world&mdash;a false teacher,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> be hailed as a friend, and no\n  man would seek my life.<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> But if all religious teachers were honest enough to renounce their\n  pretensions to godliness<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> when their ignorance of the knowledge of God is made manifest,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> they\n  will all be as badly off as I am, at any rate; and you might as well take the lives of other false\n  teachers as that of mine, if I am false. If any man is authorized to take away my life because he\n  thinks and says I am a false teacher, then, upon the same principle, we should be justified in taking\n  away the life of every false teacher, and where would be the end of blood? And who would not be\n  the sufferer?<span class=\"textFootRef\">a<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Privilege of Religious Freedom<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">But meddle not<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> with any man for his religion:<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> and all governments ought to permit every\n  man to enjoy his religion unmolested.<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> No man is authorized to take away life in consequence of\n  difference of religion, which all laws and governments ought to tolerate and protect, right or wrong.\n  Every man has a natural, and, in our country, a constitutional right to be a false prophet,<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> as well\n  as a true prophet. If I show, verily, that<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108862\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108862)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108862)\">John 17:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116388\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116388)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116388)\">D&amp;C 132:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107394\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107394)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107394)\">Jer. 31:34<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106778\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106778)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106778)\">Ps. 77:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106981\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106981)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106981)\">Eccl. 1:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112956\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112956)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112956)\">Moro. 7:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114997\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114997)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114997)\">D&amp;C 90:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107902\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107902)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107902)\">Matt. 7:33 (JST)<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116389\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116389)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116389)\">D&amp;C 132:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114846\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114846)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114846)\">D&amp;C 88:49<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109634\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109634)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109634)\">2 Cor. 1:22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109778\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109778)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109778)\">Eph. 1:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114443\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114443)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114443)\">D&amp;C 76:53<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107433\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107433)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107433)\">Lam. 2:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106603\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106603)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106603)\">Job 21:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113775\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113775)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113775)\">D&amp;C 42:81<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114336\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114336)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114336)\">D&amp;C 71:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107830\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107830)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107830)\">Matt. 5:11-12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106248\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106248)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106248)\">Num. 12:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106541\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106541)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106541)\">2 Chr. 32:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115556\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115556)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115556)\">D&amp;C 109:29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115754\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115754)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115754)\">D&amp;C 121:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110545\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110545)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110545)\">2 Pet. 2:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111481\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111481)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111481)\">W of M 1:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106444\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106444)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106444)\">1 Kgs. 10:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106706\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106706)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106706)\">Ps. 38:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111144\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111144)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111144)\">2 Ne. 5:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112480\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112480)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112480)\">Hel. 9:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110064\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110064)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110064)\">2 Tim. 3:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117104\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117104)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117104)\">JS&mdash;H 1:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110580\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110580)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110580)\">1 Jn. 2:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114164\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114164)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114164)\">D&amp;C 63:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106959\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106959)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106959)\">Prov. 24:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116539\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116539)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116539)\">D&amp;C 134:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116515\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116515)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116515)\">D&amp;C 134:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116516\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116516)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116516)\">D&amp;C 134:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107882\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107882)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107882)\">Matt. 7:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108204\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108204)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108204)\">Matt. 24:11,24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109083\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109083)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109083)\">Acts 13:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110546\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110546)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110546)\">2 Pet. 2:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110821\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110821)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110821)\">Rev. 16:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111482\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111482)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111482)\">W of M 1:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112500\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112500)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112500)\">Hel. 13:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112762\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112762)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112762)\">4 Ne. 1:34<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"textFootnotes\">\n    \n      <p class=\"std\"><span class=\"textMark\">a<\/span>These remarks will be better understood, if it is remembered that about this time the storms of a renewed persecution were bursting upon the Prophet, and his life was threatened upon every side.<\/p>\n    \n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}